Wash and dry all produce.

Slice @Fresh Mozzarella{4%ounce} and @Roma Tomato{1} into ¼-inch-thick rounds. Season tomato with @Salt{} and @Pepper{}. Halve @Ciabatta Bread{2}. Toast until golden, if desired.

In a #small bowl{}, combine @Pesto{2%ounce} and @Mayonnaise{1%ounce}; spread onto cut sides of ciabatta. Fill with tomato, @Prosciutto{2%ounce}, and mozzarella.

Cut sandwiches on a diagonal.